README: 
Following are the step by step instruction for starting the system:

For any intersection follow the below intructions:

1. Compile and run the Controller
	C = g++ -o <controller> controller.cpp -lpcap -lpthread
	R = ./<controller> <logfile.txt>

2. Compile and run the Forwarder
	C = g++ -o <forwarder> forwarder.cpp -lpcap -lpthread
	R = ./<forwarder> <logfile.txt>

3. Compile and run the input nodes
	C = g++ -o <node*> inputnode.cpp -lpcap -lpthread
	R = ./<node*> <dir> <SID> <distribution>
	*dir = N/S/E/W
	*SID = 1/2/3
	*distribution = CBR (0), Poisson (1)

** Ignore Step 4 if not applicable
4. Compile and run the common nodes
	C = g++ <node*> common.cpp -lpcap -lpthread
	R = ./<node*> <DIR1> <DIR2> <SID>
	*DIR1 - DIR2 = "E W" / "N S"
	*SID = 1/2/3

5. Compile and run the I-nodes
	C = g++ -o <nodeI*> nodeI.cpp -lpcap -lpthread
	R = ./<nodeI> <DIR> <FWD_INT> <logfile.txt>
	*DIR = direction of the I-node
	FWD_INT = 0000NESW

Run every intersection in the above order and enjoy

